## Python environment

This project uses [`uv`](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/).

```bash
uv sync                 # install deps
uv run <command>        # run in the project venv
uv run ruff check .     # lint
uv run ruff format .    # format
uv run pytest           # tests
```
{{/if}}

{{#if lightrag}}
## LightRAG memory

Agent memory is indexed by [LightRAG](https://github.com/hkuds/lightrag), backed by the working directory at [`memory/.lightrag/`](memory/.lightrag/) (gitignored).

- Ingest session logs and vault notes: `./scripts/ingest_sessions.py`
- Query memory: `./scripts/query_memory.py "<question>"`

Both scripts are deterministic wrappers around LightRAG — the LLM is only invoked inside LightRAG itself for entity extraction and synthesis.
{{/if}}

## Adding new MCPs later

Edit [`config.yaml`](config.yaml) and run the corresponding `claude mcp add …` command. See [`scripts/mcp-manage.sh`](scripts/mcp-manage.sh) for convenience wrappers.

## Reset or re-init

Re-run `/project-init` (or `project-init` from shell) in this project to re-select options. It will not overwrite existing memory or vault content.
